reviews.review_text: Skip this source Here's my advice: skip this and just download the other source here, the FOB.  It's WAAAYYYY better.  There's no need to listen to this.  This is a solid, and in my opinion underrated show from '88, and this source doesn't do it justice.
This is a board?!?!? Why is this source even up here?  This is without question the lousiest sounding SBD I've EVER heard.  ANY of the AUDs of this show are better than this recording, trust me.
